title: [EUW][Diamond][S] Looking to form serious League team
body:
Hey!

We are currently looking to form a serious League team and are looking for players in all positions. If you have a competitive spirit and want to be part of a group that is looking to improve individually and as a team please join the following discord channel and pm me so we can have a chat.
You should be at least Diamond in either flexQ or soloQ, have a lot of game knowledge and experience. Players with competitive experience are highly preferred.

https://discord.gg/fxK82uC [Pyrana]
